Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.76,0:00:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you something, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A present.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't have our hot pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.42,0:00:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Still want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.09,0:00:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, but when?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Any time will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Any time? What about work?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.13,0:00:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been suspended.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm unemployed for two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Because you hit my professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry. I'm really just so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a problem. Stop worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a silent night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eclipse was beginnin'
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:00:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The overlapping moments
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We might believe them to be eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's darker than black
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The labyrinthine sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.51,0:01:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Begs for light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I bite your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.76,0:01:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The impulse eats away at me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.76,0:01:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I... Can I... Can I... Who am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Libido erases my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Into darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.67,0:01:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have fallen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking a hideous form
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If my human tears have dried
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you think of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Our crimson blood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NOur crimson blood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wets our bond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We share our weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NWe share our weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we two live on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Licking each other's wounds
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Defining each other's life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirsting for love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Paradox
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you since winter break started!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't give me any attention anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume this means you have a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What? For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but... W-we're not exactly dating...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but from the look on your face,\NI'm guessing it's going pretty well!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So spill! What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,C-come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not! Last I heard, men totally freaked you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:02:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he cute? How'd you meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not very friendly,\Nand he often gets angry with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's really very nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's willing to admit when he's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and he can jump really high!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? Is he in track and field or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, no, but... something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And... I met him on the way home one night...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been coming over after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make dinner and we'll eat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You let him in your house\Nand feed him dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that's a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he a decent guy? Can you trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I think I can trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,W-well, if you're that sure, then I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I house this filthy devil inside me, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I act like I'm some knight in shining armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Yanagi. How have things been?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come see me sometime after New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for your physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Sakaki's hosting his usual\NNew Year's party at the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a wife and kids, so I won't be there,\Nbut all the singles should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out if you feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I got carried away. I bought too much stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling kind of out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because I didn't get any sleep last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot pot with Anzai on New Year's Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,J-just thinking about it makes me blush!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,O-ow...\NI-I'm sorry! Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry! Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I really am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Miss, I'm in a hurry, so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yipe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You... you startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you went to the store already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just, your face looks kind of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, it's not a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we get a lot of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want too much snow.\NThen you have to shovel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I can carry that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I guess it doesn't snow that much in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Authorities are still on the lookout\Nfor a man who disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4}Restaurant Murder, Man Goes Missing\Nafter a stabbing at a restaurant earlier today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from Hokkaido?\NAccording to the manager who found the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Around Obihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:06:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, didn't you want to go home for New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I never go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,D-did I ask something I shouldn't have?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stab wounds were found in\Nmultiple places on the victim's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Could be the work of a devil.\NStab wounds were found in\Nmultiple places on the victim's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Could be the work of a devil.\Nand it is believed that loss of blood\Nwas the direct cause of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and it is believed that loss of blood\Nwas the direct cause of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Vampires tend to stab their victims after a kill,\Nto hide any signs that they drank the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'd suspect the missing man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, because if he's missing,\Nthat means he ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't say for sure, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If the fugitive really is a devil,\Nhe may be around here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But that restaurant is pretty far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Devils have excellent physical abilities.\NAnd they run fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, did you know that guy at the store?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He was suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I didn't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But he seemed nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You are way too trusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But he picked up my vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Picking up vegetables makes you a good person?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but maybe he did look kind of like a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes him even more dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean he had dark circles under his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he had drunk any blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How...? You really know your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't know the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,M-meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I have to work on New Year's Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when the person of interest is a devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, we're still waiting for the autopsy results.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:07:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you folks detectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my employees, Katagiri, he's a vampire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the guy that did it!\NGet out there and arrest him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're Mr. Okino, the manager, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know for sure who did it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's to know?\NShe had no blood in her body, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It had to be a vampire! What else could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, sir, just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it that I smell blood\Ncoming from your entire body?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you're making stuff up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My sense of smell is a little better than average.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans only reek this badly of blood\Nwhen they've been drenched in someone else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you're a devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? What is it? I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki, is there a wanted devil on the loose?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah, the suspect in the restaurant stabbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks like he was framed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's innocent?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the autopsy, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:09:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The killer made it look like a devil did it,\Nby causing massive blood loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't identified him yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's a devil nearby\Nwho seems to be running from-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't feed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Name and age?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Oryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your real name. In full.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryunosuke Katagiri, age 36.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's our guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll send a car to get him. Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Those circles under his eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your boyfriend a devil, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,H-he's not my boy-!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your objection? And he's not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're spending New Year's Eve together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were framed, you shouldn't need to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So why did you come all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me an honest answer,\Nand you can have some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Devils run faster than humans. And we're stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If we get in a little fight, we might end up\Nbeating the other guy half to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I hit a man and he started bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I felt the urge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I hated that man, but I sucked his blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So I made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never hurt a human again,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and if I feel like I might, I get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The murder victim was a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She was the only one there\Nwho treated me like a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to become a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the hot pot. It was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the girlfriend? She's just a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Jill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she beat me in chest-size.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come see me sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:10:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell I'd go to her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman looked like a Hollywood movie star.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she was really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so? I think she's average.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Wh-why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it what she said? About going to see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just... you know, one-sided.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,These stairs are killing me!\NShe was just saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You bought too much to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of that's for you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't drink wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... feel so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I was jealous of that beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And... and I didn't even know your first name, Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've dreamed of this. More than once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I really am pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Always doing things like this in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know I'm nowhere near good enough for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face is redder than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who's pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell she wasn't feeling well,\Nbut I ignored it, and now look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4}2013 Is Almost Here!\N{\an4}The Countdown Begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here looking at the holiday lights\Nat Sapporo Odori Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Hokkaido.\NThe place is packed with visitors\Nwaiting for the big countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The place is packed with visitors\Nwaiting for the big countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}I'd like to go there someday.\NThe place is packed with visitors\Nwaiting for the big countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get myself a sedative.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready for the countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten. Nine. Eight. Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I saying? "I'll take you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Five. Four.\NWhat am I saying? "I'll take you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Three. Two. One!\NShe's a human. I'm a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a human. I'm a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shot through the head with a 7.62mm bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Died instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the fifth one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Jill, take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I already did!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw the blood and didn't transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means this one isn't human, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Can't you be\Ngentlemanly enough to ask if I'm okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww. Poor girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night's victim makes five\Nin this series of shootings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All with a single shot to the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And the victims are all devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Devils?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But not one of them was in\Na transformed state when they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They looked just like normal humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So the killer knew they were devils?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Assuming that's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,then how did the shooter know\Nthe victims were devils?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That information is exclusive to city halls,\Ninsurance companies, hospitals, and the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some devil dating sites, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\NYou got a date or something, Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How far have you gone with her, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Touch her boobs yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have to broadcast your stupid questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, I really want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How does one go about dating a human woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The sight of blood arouses you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you're aroused,\Nyou want to see more blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even feel her up without being very careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like that! And quit it with the hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:14:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it's driving you crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be happy to help you... let off some steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why I asked Anzai here,\Neven though he's suspended?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a list of devils going around,\Nthen either of you could be the next target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Awww. Are you worried about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm saying I don't have time to babysit you.\NSo watch yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They are like children, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yanagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I might find my patient here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take my physical another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't forget, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to see me after New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I bet you're running low on sedatives, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,One? You shouldn't be going through them that fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So when are you coming, Anzai?!\NI want a specific date! Today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's not good. Tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, then! Ten in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,His gangster roots are showing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A list of devils...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the devil population, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it? 0.01%? Sawazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's about the percentage here in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Roughly a thousand in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere between\Nnear-threatened and endangered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that sex between humans and devils is legal,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing we'll be seeing even fewer purebloods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You could let Yanagi watch,\Nthen you can screw your girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your mind out of the gutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I still haven't gotten her that Christmas present.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot.\NYou can see your girlfriend if you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but hold off on the jumping telephone poles\Nfor a while. You'll attract attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! I'm walking, okay? On the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how you like jumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, I'm hanging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheese-stuffed cabbage rolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty good idea, if I do say so myself.\NShould be tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he should be getting home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, "getting home"? Why would I say it that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're sure you can trust this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You had virtually no interest in men before now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And you haven't known him that long, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,R-right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be too careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens, talk to me. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like she's my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's right.\NWe haven't known each other that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I only met him two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not even his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel like I hardly know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why he keeps coming to my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could it be? A delivery?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai always comes in through the balcony, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... whaa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to see you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but why are you at my front door?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I do that sometimes, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! The rice is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having cabbage rolls today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I tweaked the recipe, and I think it'll be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,H-how am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! I'm all better!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fever's gone? But your hand is hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, yours is just too cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're 80 degrees, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are all devils that cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you go out today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No, just to the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But something seems... different about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I... I did put on some makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The next one gets your head, monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai! Anzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No. But you, Anzai-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your head down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd it come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How long were they after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that... why were they after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm a devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.21,0:20:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill!\NAre you... okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}I know it's late,\N{\an5}but Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I lose him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me, you monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you after, murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your kind are the murderers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You pretend to care just long enough\Nto get your chance to drink our blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother died because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you devils never existed, she'd still be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.21,0:21:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To make sure you never kill again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I hate you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Like softly melting away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could have loved each other more like that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What could I have told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.21,0:22:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A chance encounter that cannot amount to love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.67,0:22:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone forgive me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this filthy form is who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.63,0:22:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.84,0:22:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these fingers trembling as they touch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story of fighting together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hold you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to protect you without hurting you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.63,0:22:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You and only you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story of desiring forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I will keep fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.05,0:22:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Against the urges surging up inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, again, I..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.13,0:23:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep red dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Like we're softly melting away...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.67,0:23:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're weaker than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You a civilian?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.09,0:23:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.05,0:23:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,DEVILS' LINE:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Line 4,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.59,0:23:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"Monster."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.05,0:23:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Monster